        </para>
        <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
          <text>Omit from <citation jurisdiction="nz">Part <extref href="DLM314308">1</extref> of Schedule 1</citation> the items relating to <citation jurisdiction="nz">sections <extref href="DLM329081">130 to 142</extref> of the <leg-title href="DLM327381">Crimes Act 1961</leg-title></citation> and substitute:</text>
